@startuml
title Schedule Fetch Sequence

actor User
participant MainWindow
participant OutlookCalendarService
participant "Outlook Desktop(COM)" as Outlook
participant MainWindowViewModel

User -> MainWindow : Click "Fetch Schedule"
MainWindow -> OutlookCalendarService : GetTodayEventsAsync()
OutlookCalendarService -> Outlook : Acquire Outlook.Application
OutlookCalendarService -> Outlook : Get default calendar
OutlookCalendarService -> Outlook : Restrict by today range
Outlook --> OutlookCalendarService : Event list
OutlookCalendarService --> MainWindow : CalendarEventItem[]
MainWindow -> MainWindowViewModel : UpdateScheduleRanges(timedEvents)
MainWindow -> MainWindow : RenderCalendarEvents(allEvents)
MainWindow --> User : Refresh list and clock bands
@enduml
